<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Helvetica;  "><img src="http://7xotew.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/article-157-1.jpg" title="京都祗园附近性价比超高住宿推荐_图片_1" alt="京都祗园附近性价比超高住宿推荐_图片_1"></p>
